{
  "stem": "15576.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I remembered that my-- that the Russians, they were called at that time, they were antisemitic at the time, no?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they came to my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted to take his horse away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know whether he disputed it or not, but they killed him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They killed my grandfather, my mother's mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- I'm named after him, so that was 1917, '18, somewhere around there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I still went to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During-- during the Russian occupation, we didn't have good food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember my mother's two sisters were a little bit well-off to do, and they gave us a cow And food for the cow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had at least milk and cheese, not too much rationed, but we had it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From-- from his voyage, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From the beginning, yeah, we got mail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got a mail before my father reached Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "May-- maybe you check out and maybe the whole family came out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you can imagine my father's feeling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was afraid to ask him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And here, this letter comes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From his-- from his brother, to try to do whatever we can.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was too late.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We get papers, three times to go get papers with the Polish government, papers with the Russian government.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They even tried through the German government.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I might as well mention, three months after he went-- well, Poland was still-- 1938 or '39.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had papers to go through Japan, to go there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my father went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was in the States, already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through-- through Japan to the United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then the war broke out with-- it didn't go-- it went against me, whatever we did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I took a lot of it out on my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
